課程概述 Course Description
       西洋經濟史課程之目標在於扼要的勾勒出西洋（特別是歐洲國家）長期的經濟發展脈絡（由上古時期到二十世紀）。課程內容除了著重於探討西方社會從古至今的經濟活動特色及經濟結構的變遷，並分析重要經濟事件所產生的影響與問題。The target of the western economic history is to delineate the western (Europe) economic development from the ancient to 1970’s. The main points are the process of historical economic evolution and structural variation, including special topics of interest.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To understand the history of global long-term economic developmentTo realize western nations' economic structure in different periodTo analyze European countries' economic impacts upon Asia-pacific region To discuss economic fluctuations and the creation of economic globalization 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1課程介紹與西洋經濟史導論 
(Course Introduction and Overview)2長期經濟發展理論暨古代經濟本質 (Theory of Stages o Economic Developemt and Economic Nature in Ancient Times)3環地中海地區的古文明經濟史 (Ancient Economic Civilizations in the Mediterranean World)4中世紀封建制度與莊園制度 (Feudalism and the Manorial System in the Middle Ages)5歐洲中世紀後期的經濟發展與變革(一): 拜占庭及阿拉伯世界 (Economic Development and Evolution in the late Medieval Period (I): Byzantium and Arabic Empires)6中世紀後期的經濟發展與變革(二):西歐的經濟復甦 (Economic Development and Evolution in the late Medieval Period (II): Western Europe's Economic Revival)7重商主義暨大航海時代(一): 遠洋貿易的興起 (Mercantilism and the Age of Exploration (I): the Rise of Oceanic Trade)8重商主義暨大航海時代 (二): 重商主義 (Mercantilism and the Age of Exploration (II): Mercantilism)9期中考 Midterm Exam.10近代初期的農業、工藝及商貿金融發展與革新 (The Newly-Development and Innovation of Agriculture, Industry ad financial System in the Early Modern Period) 11十八、十九世紀工業(產業)革命 (The Industrial Revolution in the Eighteenth and Nineteenth Centuries)12十六十九世紀美洲經濟展 (American Economic Development between the 16th and 19th Centuries)13十九世紀後期的全球經濟新發展與變革 (Global Economic Development and Fluctuations in the late 19th Century)14戰爭與和平: 第一次世界大戰後的經濟局勢和經濟大恐慌 (War and Peace: The Economic Consequences of the WWI and the Great Depression)15第二次世界大戰暨戰後經濟重建與成長 (The Economics of World War II and Postwar Economic Settlements and Growth)16石油危機暨二十世紀末期的經濟變動與新發展 (The Oil Crises and the further Economic Development in the last Decades of the Twentieth Century)17當代資本主義社會的經濟發展趨勢與危機 (Economic Developmental Trend and Crisis in the Contemporary Capitalist World)18Final Exam. 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


